NAME
  ahm -- acyclic complexity measure

SYNOPSIS
  ahm [-a] [-c] [-f] [-h] [-q] [-v]

DESCRIPTION
  Static code complexity analyser for c-family syntax (C, C++, Java, ECMAScript, C#, &c)
  it parses conditions of a standard data input stream (stdin) for leveraging an absolute number.

  Options available:
  -a          acyclic complexity, regards nested c-family syntax (O(n^2)
  -c          cyclomatic complexity, condition count (O(n))
  -f          control flow sub path conjecture O(2n)
  -h, --help  show this help message
  -q          all sub paths O(2^n)
  -v          verify condition paths
